assoc_norm
----------

l1: $ (f o g) o h ~ f o (g o h) $ by comp_assoc []

unit_norm
---------

l1: $ id o f ~ f $ by comp_unit []

pb_preserves_mono
-----------------

l0: $ f_ o p1 ~ g_ o p2 $ by pb_square []
l1: $ f_ o (p1 o alpha) ~ g_ o (p2 o alpha) $ by comp_right (f := $ f_ o p1 $, g := $ g_ o p2 $, h := $ alpha $) [l0]
l2: $ f_ o (p1 o beta) ~ g_ o (p2 o beta) $ by comp_right (f := $ f_ o p1 $, g := $ g_ o p2 $, h := $ beta $) [l0]
l3: $ g_ o (p2 o alpha) ~ g_ o (p2 o beta) $ by comp_left (f := $ p2 o alpha $, g := $ p2 o beta $, h := $ g_ $) [#1]
l4: $ f_ o (p1 o alpha) ~ g_ o (p2 o beta) $ by mor_trans [l1, l3]
l5: $ g_ o (p2 o beta) ~ f_ o (p1 o beta) $ by mor_sym [l2]
l6: $ f_ o (p1 o alpha) ~ f_ o (p1 o beta) $ by mor_trans [l4, l5]
l7: $ p1 o alpha ~ p1 o beta $ by f_mono [l6]
l8: $ p1 o alpha ~ p1 o alpha $ by mor_refl []
l9: $ p2 o alpha ~ p2 o alpha $ by mor_refl []
l10: $ alpha ~ pb_med (p1 o alpha) (p2 o alpha) $ by pb_med_unique [l8, l9]
l11: $ p1 o beta ~ p1 o beta $ by mor_refl []
l12: $ p2 o beta ~ p2 o beta $ by mor_refl []
l13: $ beta ~ pb_med (p1 o beta) (p2 o beta) $ by pb_med_unique [l11, l12]
l14: $ pb_med (p1 o alpha) (p2 o alpha) ~ pb_med (p1 o beta) (p2 o beta) $ by pb_med_congr [l7, #1]
l15: $ alpha ~ pb_med (p1 o beta) (p2 o beta) $ by mor_trans [l10, l14]
l16: $ pb_med (p1 o beta) (p2 o beta) ~ beta $ by mor_sym [l13]
l17: $ alpha ~ beta $ by mor_trans [l15, l16]
